  "title": "Cook (Japanese Cuisine) (Up to $3500 / Islandwide)",
  "description": "<p>Job Title: Cook (Japanese Cuisine) ID6024<br>\nLocation: Islandwide<br>\nWorking Hours: Retail hour 44hrs/week +OT<br>\nSalary: $2800- $3500<br>\n<br>\nRoles &amp; Responsibilities:<br>\n• Prepare, cook, pack, and label food (including sashimi) while ensuring freshness and correct portions.<br>\n• Maintain cleanliness, food safety, and proper storage of ingredients.<br>\n• Welcome customers and provide good service.<br>\n• Monitor stock levels and reorder when needed.<br>\n• Train junior staff to maintain quality standards.<br>\n<br>\nJob Requirements<br>\n• Good communication and teamwork.<br>\n• Strong hygiene practices and food safety knowledge.<br>\n• Food hygiene certificate required.<br>\n<br>\nBenefits<br>\n• Variable bonus<br>\n• Overtime pay<br>\n• Staff discount<br>\n• Birthday leave &amp; voucher<br>\n• Medical benefits</p>",
